answers.body_markdown:
univocity-parsers is your best bet on loading the CSV file, you probably won&#39;t be able to hand code anything faster. The problems you are having come from possibly 2 things:

1 - loading everything in memory. That&#39;s generally a bad design decision, but if you do that make sure to have enough memory allocated for your application. Give it more memory 
using flags `-Xms8G` and `Xmx8G` for example.

2 - you are probably not batching your insert statements.

My suggestion is to try this (using univocity-parsers):

        //configure input format using
		CsvParserSettings settings = new CsvParserSettings();
		
